author: davsclaus
msg: CAMEL-3535: Use a copy of the incoming exchange for aggregation without sharing UoW. This ensures that on compleiton on the completed exchange always will be executed. This ensures the aggregation repository will always be confirmed, and the internal in progress map will have the completed exchange removed as well, preventing it from eating memory over time.
